Text.Text: If you are really that interested, we've transmitted a mission waypoint over to your Flight officer.
It was huge! I wouldn't recommend [Topic:going near it] if I were you.
We just narrowly evaded something and are happy to be here to [Topic:talk about it]!
We were on our way here and we detected [Topic:something big] on our long range sensors. It started an approach vector on us so we high tailed it out of there!
Trust me, you don't want to hear about it!

Imperial-Yes.Text: Yes we do. Please tell us more!

Imperial-No.Text: Your right, I think we'll pass.

Imperial-NoWay.Text: No thank you. Plausible deniability you know...

Text.Text: It wasn't that far. We will trasmit the coordinates to your flight officer. Good hunting!
No. I don't think it's a good idea!
We nearly had a run in with them over in a [Topic:nearby system]
We are making a civilian delivery, and just happy to be avoiding any [Topic:Imperial entanglements]

available_missions.Name: The Long Patrol
available_missions.Description:
Patrol several key star systems during a routine patrol and check in on various Comm Stations to ensure they are safe.

A good starter mission for beginners.

available_missions.Name: The Art of Detente
available_missions.Description: A operations ship has become disabled and is stranded in enemy territory. Can the Horizons get them out safely?

available_missions.Name: The Borderlands
available_missions.Description:
Tensions are at the breaking point near the Alliance-Daichi border. Two stations stand opposed with many outposts in-between. The first to control all eight outposts or destroy the enemy base wins.

Who will be victorious?

available_missions.Name: The Borderlands (3 Team)
available_missions.Description:
Tensions are at the breaking point near the Alliance-Daichi border. Three stations stand opposed with many outposts in-between. The first to control all eight outposts or destroy all other enemy bases wins.

Who will be victorious?

available_missions.Name: The Homestead Company
available_missions.Description:
The Homestead Company has requested an escort to help them get to Chara Proxima. Lead their convoy to the safety of their new home.

A great mix of action and deduction.

available_missions.Name: Hot Pursuit
available_missions.Description: A stolen capitol ship and no time to waste. Catch the Daichi criminals before they can complete their mission.

available_missions.Name: Daichi Invasion
available_missions.Description:
Survive wave after wave of enemy ships as you defend 4 stations from their assault. Difficulty increases with each wave. 
    
A great mission for an action hungry crew.

available_missions.Name: The Last Horizon
available_missions.Description: I wonder what's happening over at Mars...

available_missions.Name: Open Playground
available_missions.Description:
First Star To The Right, And Straight On Until Morning...
    
Explore the universe in a fighter with no enemies.

available_missions.Name: Radical Action
available_missions.Description: The new Opal Bay outpost and mining operations are almost complete. Assist Alliance command in getting these facilities finished.

available_missions.Name: What Lies Beyond Mars
available_missions.Description:
Can you withstand the assault from a squadron of Daichi DARTs that never give up? 
    
*** This Is A Sample Fighter Mission ***

available_missions.Name: The Wrong Place, The Wrong Time
available_missions.Description:
It might just be a case of the Mondays... 

At least your last Monday...

ordnance.Name: Wasp [Fast]
ordnance.Description: Very fast and nimble, but not as strong as other missiles.
